,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:13:56.000Z","msg":"讀中二有男友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n新北市真係贏晒"},{"pid":"42abbe3ad6687c68b8bf169e61216f1304b05e77","tid":601012,"uid":158270,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:15:13.000Z","msg":"點解未成年人冇搞野嘅權利？"},{"pid":"df04b13484388843ff6ecd44602c6eed52f5d36d","tid":601012,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"749c21b612a14c9ce0bd0dcbddc4b88eb1abd330","tid":601012,"uid":46356,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:43:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直到去年大女兒讀國中二年級時，向男友透露父親所為，男友轉告學校輔導老師，才揭發這名獸父惡行。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n國中二年級，即係香港Form 2年紀？<br />\n<br />\nForm 2就交男友<br />\n如果o係香港，警方分分鐘會調查埋個男友"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:16:12.000Z","msg":"擺到明條仔唔明點解條女技術咁好啦"},{"pid":"db6479e2b2d730dae6604300fc5ca32587d29138","tid":601012,"uid":47954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:26:51.000Z","msg":"所"},{"pid":"be3ef2f6cc539c1fd79d052366dcc63d4cc32e11","tid":601012,"uid":93752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:32:14.000Z","msg":"又台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6d9769cfe52e3745108b0a986a7fdb0e9c47b1","tid":601012,"uid":63715,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:36:15.000Z","msg":"咁耐都未有人貼潮文   等我黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以咪話，台灣真係一個充滿住bitch同厹既地方，呢個地方既人成個腦除左諗點樣恥笑香港叫支那之外 <br />\n就係諗住做愛，sex，做愛，外遇，偷情，同人妻人夫做愛，亂倫， 強姦，迷姦，撿屍<br />\n一有時間就諗下可以點樣屌到自己個呀嫂，堂/表姐妹，女朋友/老婆嘅姊妹，或者朋友個女，朋友個孫，弱智信徒嘅弱智女、 弱智孫女，老闆屌女秘書，醫生屌女病人，偷嘢女客人主動叫處男店員屌佢同幫佢口交 <br />\n老師就想同自己個學生做下愛咁，學生又諗下點屌個大波miss <br />\n再唔係就係最鍾意做愛果時拍下片，方便以後分手再要脅下個前度做多幾次分手愛 <br />\n台妹最馨同條仔吵兩句嘴就馬上搵前度傾心事，傾傾下就又做愛 <br />\n個前度問佢可唔可以內射，台妹搖頭說不，但最後還是被射滿滿 <br />\n所以話，呢個地方真係十分淫亂"},{"pid":"661460def0596691045ebb180c57296a1e4d7ed3","tid":601012,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:42:23.000Z","msg":"數住幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8d9d5db028f2016d3248ca08d157cc40cb4fe5","tid":601012,"uid":17420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df04b13484388843ff6ecd44602c6eed52f5d36d","tid":601012,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"749c21b612a14c9ce0bd0dcbddc4b88eb1abd330","tid":601012,"uid":46356,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:43:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直到去年大女兒讀國中二年級時，向男友透露父親所為，男友轉告學校輔導老師，才揭發這名獸父惡行。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n國中二年級，即係香港Form 2年紀？<br />\n<br />\nForm 2就交男友<br />\n如果o係香港，警方分分鐘會調查埋個男友"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:16:12.000Z","msg":"擺到明條仔唔明點解條女技術咁好啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:43:41.000Z","msg":"為什麼你這麼熟練！！"},{"pid":"278fd074eec6ea843a479f917c4800bb631db0f1","tid":601012,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8f6e70add880cdb7190d8e0aff60153687b4bb8","tid":601012,"uid":46356,"like":4,"dislike":25,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:47:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又係新北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>日日都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟係咩<span style=\"color: red;\">國家</span>先可以咁</blockquote><br />\n咁即係入&ldquo;中國&rdquo;條數喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:48:16.000Z","msg":"你叫D五毛點駁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa10f195d27c108f24988841b5d710831e2fc38","tid":601012,"uid":47954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd8d9d5db028f2016d3248ca08d157cc40cb4fe5","tid":601012,"uid":17420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df04b13484388843ff6ecd44602c6eed52f5d36d","tid":601012,"uid":33874,"like